Package codebrains.crazysellout.Models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountModel
    Class that contains methods to checks the integrity of new account before it is registered inside the database.
    AddProductModel
    Class that contains proper methods to check the integrity of product addition before the new product is registered inside the database.
    CalculateDistanceModel
    Class that calculates the distance between a single product object and the user and if it is inside the selected distance area (its selected by the user) the this specific product is added inside a json array to be later displayed into the map.
    FavoritesModel
    Class that handles the display of all the favorite products of the user into a list.
    LoginModel
    Class that contains proper methods to check the integrity of the new product before it is added to the database.
    ProductList
    Class that initialize the expandable list in the activity from the response that the server returned.
    UserProfileUpdateModel
    Class that contains methods valid for checking the update user profile data.
